27
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:41,330
When they give me the money,

28
00:01:41,330 --> 00:01:42,560
I'll give you everything, okay?

29
00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:46,480
As long as you let me go,

30
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,920
