35
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,680
Do you know what it is?

36
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,680
As long as you let me go,

37
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:01,990
I'll give you whatever you want.

38
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,760
I want the life of Zhao Zhiqian,

39
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:17,360
who is your biggest buyer.

40
00:02:38,740 --> 00:02:39,590
Master,

41
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:40,880
how should we handle the orphans?

42
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:44,920
How many informants

43
