44
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:47,760
Ten.

45
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,990
Then double the replacements.

46
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:53,240
Send them all to the unit.

47
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,360
What time is it now?

48
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:56,600
Just after seven.

49
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,280
Notify Rong Yin

50
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,060
that honored guest is arriving.

51
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,840
Prepare for a bath.

52
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:34,440
Tonight, we have only one guest.

53
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:37,880
Are you satisfied

54
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,320
