61
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,440
Master,

62
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,440
are you a chess player

63
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:06,080
or an onlooker?

64
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,480
Living in a fleeting dream,

65
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,720
no one knows who Lu Sheng is.

66
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,440
Governor,

67
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,560
would you like to grab a drink?

68
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,320
Since we're having a drink,

69
00:04:17,880 --> 00:04:19,520
why don't you show your true face?

70
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,480
Zheng,

71
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,140
hope you've been well.

72
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,280
Tang.

73
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,560
It's mine.

74
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:10,680
♪In the dark night, I fell into your eyes♪

75
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:13,360
This is raw. You can't eat.

76
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:17,540
♪Deeply buried in the first dream♪

77
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:21,240
♪Listening to boat whistles and river breeze♪

78
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:24,320
♪Breeze touches my collar, sunset glows♪

79
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:29,340
♪Hope is carried along the way♪

80
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,200
This is for you.

81
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:36,560
♪Amidst the chaos, I lose my naivety♪

82
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:44,080
♪Only then I understand life's upheavals♪

83
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:47,180
♪Like soaring geese meet the endless sky♪

84
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:48,040
Take it.

85
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:51,160
♪Like sparks that stir the spring breeze♪

86
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:57,800
♪No longer adrift,
no longer trapped in cages♪

87
00:05:58,200 --> 00:06:04,160
♪If the world loses all its colors♪

88
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:06,720
♪There will always be someone who wakes up♪

89
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:10,920
♪Transforming into light and shining bright♪

90
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,880
♪Please listen closely♪

91
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,520
You...

92
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,160
Why are you following me?

93
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:24,480
♪Everyone's alive, no one is dust♪

94
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:26,920
Because

95
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:30,080
I have nowhere to go.

96
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:33,320
♪Flowers will bloom someday♪

97
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,400
From now on,

98
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,320
I'll protect you.

99
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,600
♪Please, for me♪

100
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:44,560
♪Set reunion words beyond the crowd♪

101
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:47,880
♪Unchanged by time♪

102
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:53,400
♪The torch is our existence♪

103
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,280
Tang,

104
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,120
I finally found you.

105
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,890
I've been looking for you these five years.

106
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,280
But no news of you.

107
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,840
Now, we

108
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,400
can be together again.

109
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,440
Zheng,

110
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,880
I see you're doing well now.

111
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,920
I'm truly happy for you.

112
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,560
Tang, do you have any wine?

113
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:23,200
Let's drink together all night

114
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:24,360
and have a good time.

115
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:26,640
Come on.

116
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:32,120
Come on.

117
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,680
Tonight,

118
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,520
we only have this bottle.

119
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,040
Back in the day,

120
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,200
you and I shared the same meal.

121
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,160
You keep distant with me now.

122
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,080
Let's have a drink.

123
00:07:59,120 --> 00:07:59,960
Zheng.

124
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:01,600
To Heaven and Earth.

125
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,960
Finally, it shows mercy to us

126
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,980
and let us meet in Luan City.

127
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,120
I haven't been happy in a long time.

128
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:21,480
Who would've thought

129
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,280
the once fragile young man

130
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:25,840
has become the Master of Lu Sheng Tower?

131
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,880
To make a living in this chaotic place,

132
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,480
I have to do many things.

133
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,240
But, don't worry.

134
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,080
I only sell information.

135
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:38,720
That's all.

136
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,160
Don't I believe you?

137
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:47,800
Come on.

138
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,320
Tang,

139
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:03,480
do you like acting?

140
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:08,900
I remember when I was young,

141
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,280
you shared a story with me.

142
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:15,760
Lu Sheng was drunk in a fleeting dream.

143
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:17,740
I like listening to Chinese operas

144
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,340
and watching them play.

145
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,640
But I just don't enjoy acting.

146
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,760
No one in the play

147
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:30,160
can compare to Lu Sheng in my heart.

148
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,560
Tang,

149
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:41,280
do you remember the games we played as kids?

150
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,280
Come on.

151
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:57,080
When we're little, we used stones as darts.

152
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,560
You taught me that.

153
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:02,560
I wonder which one of us

154
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,290
will get the lucky draw today.

155
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,320
Tang,

156
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:20,640
I'm really happy to find you.

157
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:23,240
Zheng,

158
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,160
did you really look for me?

159
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:29,240
Of course.

160
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,200
Very good.

161
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:33,960
Now,

162
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:35,990
I should call you governor now, right?

163
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,280
Tang,

164
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:41,640
it don't matter between us.

165
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,360
It matters.

166
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:53,080
Today, I'm very happy

167
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,360
to meet you again.

168
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,560
I'll give you a gift.

169
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:09,280
Baihua Church has been closed for a long time

170
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,320
since you handled bandits.

171
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:16,280
He Molin is being hidden there.

172
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,480
Besides my people,

173
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:22,280
outsiders are also watching the He Family.

174
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,260
Compassion for people's lives.

175
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:44,720
Life is like a blooming ephemeral flower.

176
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,520
A night's fleeting fragrance.

177
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:51,920
How to face rain and wind again.

178
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:57,640
Fame and fortune, all a dream.

179
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:03,040
In dreams, my soul is intoxicated.

180
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:07,840
Awaking, we each go our separate ways.

181
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,720
A fleeting dream.

182
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:20,120
Zheng,

183
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:24,400
you told me this.

184
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,840
But you forgot it.

185
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,280
(He Zheng,)

186
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:51,160
(you are the role I most want to play.)

187
00:13:03,300 --> 00:13:05,680
♪Like a drowning whale♪

188
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:09,040
♪Falling into you♪

189
00:13:10,830 --> 00:13:13,120
♪Into every inch of your body♪

190
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:16,230
♪Then it fell apart♪

191
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:18,610
♪Without a trace♪

192
00:13:18,610 --> 00:13:20,720
♪Like a warm winter♪

193
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,390
♪Running barefoot to you♪

194
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:28,350
♪Spreading in your cold palm♪

195
00:13:28,670 --> 00:13:31,230
♪Vanishing in your warm breath♪

196
00:13:31,230 --> 00:13:34,330
♪Because nobody knows♪

197
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:37,590
♪Can't ever go back♪

198
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:41,630
♪You touch my heart, my heart♪

199
00:13:41,930 --> 00:13:44,970
♪Why is it so calm?♪

200
00:13:45,460 --> 00:13:48,450
♪Cause everybody knows♪

201
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:51,980
♪Can't ever go back♪

202
00:13:52,570 --> 00:13:56,090
♪I have long lost myself♪

203
00:13:58,200 --> 00:14:02,690
♪And lost you too♪
